These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Job: analyst, fisherman, librarian, manager
1. Job:fisherman is in an odd position##4
2. Job:manager is between Job:analyst and Job:fisherman##2
3. Job:manager is on the right of Job:analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Job   | analyst | manager | fisherman | librarian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Cigar: bluemaster, dunhill, ritmeester, game
1. Cigar:bluemaster is on the left of Cigar:game##1
2. Cigar:dunhill is in an odd position##4
3. Cigar:dunhill is on the left or right of Cigar:bluemaster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Cigar   | dunhill | bluemaster | game | ritmeester |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
