1. Birthday:january is on the left or right of Birthday:may##3
2. Birthday:may is in an odd position##4
3. Birthday:july is between Birthday:january and Birthday:october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Birthday   | may | january | july | october |

