3. Movie-Genre:drama is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:disaster##3
4. Movie-Genre:disaster is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | disaster | superhero | zombie |

