.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Music-Genre: electronic, metal, rock, hip-hop
1. Music-Genre:metal == Music-Genre:metal##1
2. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the left or right of Music-Genre:rock##3
3. Music-Genre:rock is on the far left or far right##3
4. Music-Genre:electronic is in an even position##4
5. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the left of Music-Genre:metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | hip-hop | metal | electronic |

